The paper focuses on active learning methods for instance classification problems in multiple instance learning (MIL), which are commonly used in computer vision and natural language processing applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
